<C>__{will}
<D>__{seven years.}
<C>__{chief nyback}
<D>__{seven years? where does it all go? that was some amazing time, though, wasn't it?}
<A>__{looks at will. down at his boots.}
<C>__{chief nyback }
<D>__{you haven't changed a bit, will.}
<A>__{will. looks at nyback's gut.}
